'''RTOG 03-21 ([[Radiation Oncology/Prostate|PROSTATE]])''' *''Title:'' Phase II Trial of Combined High Dose Rate Brachytherapy and External Beam Radiotherapy for Adenocarcinoma of the Prostate *''Objective:'' To estimate the rate of late Grade 3 or greater genitourinary and gastrointestinal toxicity following treatment with external beam radiation therapy and high dose rate brachytherapy *''[http://www.rtog.org/members/protocols/0321/0321.pdf Protocol]:'' 45 Gy EBRT (no IMRT) + 19 Gy (2 fractions) HDR boost *''Eligibility:'' **(cT1c-T2c and GS 2-6 and PSA 10-20) or **(cT3a-T3b and GS 2-6 and PSA <=20) or **(T1c-T3b and GS 7-10 and PSA <=20) **N0M0 *''Enrollment Target:'' 110 patients *''Activation:'' July 30, 2004
