ogressive/index.html Webcast] - "Phase III Randomized Study of Adjuvant Radiation Therapy versus Observation in Patients with Pathologic T3 Prostate Cancer (SWOG 8794)" Swanson GP et al. IJROBP Volume 63, Supplement 1 , 1 October 2005, Page S1. **'''1994''' [http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/entrez/query.fcgi?cmd=Retrieve&db=pubmed&dopt=Abstract&list_uids=7985307&query_hl=48 No Abstract] -- "An opportunity to determine optimal treatment of pT3 prostate cancer: the window may be closing." (Thompson IM, Urology 1994). <u>Review</u> **'''1992''' -- "Adjuvant Radiotherapy Following Radical Prostatectomy for Pathologic Stage C Adenocarcinoma of the Prostate: Initial Evaluation of Toxicity." I Thompson, ED Crawford, G Miller, J Paradelo, B Blumenstein, M Wolf, C Moinpour, K Hayden. American Society of Clinical Oncology 11:212 (#663), 1992.
